span> history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollRestoration<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"값","title":"값","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"auto\"><code>\"auto\"</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>페이지 내에서 사용자의 스크롤이 위치했던 장소로 복원합니다.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"manual\"><code>\"manual\"</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>스크롤을 복원하지 않습니다. 사용자가 직접 스크롤해야 합니다.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"현재_스크롤_복원_여부_알아내기","title":"현재 스크롤 복원 여부 알아내기","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> scrollRestoration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollRestoration\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scrollRestoration <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'manual'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The location on the page is not restored, user will need to scroll manually.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"스크롤_복원_비활성화","title":"스크롤 복원 비활성화","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollRestoration<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollRestoration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'manual'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"명세","id":"명세","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/history.html#dom-history-scroll-restoration-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.History.scrollRestoration"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"api.History.scrollRestoration","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/scrollRestoration/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"구문","id":"구문"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"명세","id":"명세"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"}],"summary":"History.scrollRestoration 속성을 사용하면 기록 탐색 시 사용할 스크롤 위치 복원 기능의 기본값을 웹 애플리케이션이 지정할 수 있습니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"History.scrollRestoration","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"History.scrollRestoration","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"History.scrollRestoration","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/history/scrollrestoration","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/history/scrollrestoration/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History","title":"History"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/scrollRestoration","title":"History.scrollRestoration"}],"pageTitle":"History.scrollRestoration - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}